{"tid":1591864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"929 超巨大流動連儂牆 反赤納粹大遊行","createTime":"2019-09-24T10:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T14:21:43.000Z","uid":49898,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"4da1265b0966946421780e6f0602232e6c764ff1","tid":1591864,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"雖然而家已經進入全面戰爭狀態<br />\n近排遊行集會都俾狗反對左<br />\n<br />\n但我相信929會好多人出黎<br />\n<br />\n大型和理非行動係宜家戰爭狀態下<br />\n效果其實都仲係好大<br />\n係connect到全世界<br />\n<br />\n一般人已經對連儂牆有麻木感<br />\n不過我覺得都要keep嘅<br />\n但效果上大家都知已經細左好多<br />\n<br />\n另外908美領遊行果張連儂牆<br />\n講真真係好細<br />\n同埋整大型野應該要遠距離都睇到內容<br />\n唔係就效果就大打折扣<br />\n<br />\n我有個提議<br />\n以929和理非活動做例子<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一張A3顏色紙<br />\n寫上我地嘅口號</span></span><br />\n<br />\n將遊行隊伍變成超大型流動連儂牆<br />\n我相信個視覺效果上會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再次震撼全球</span></span><br />\n我地要keep住個運動嘅溫度<br />\n就要keep住創造更多世界第一次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uuArDf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuuArDf5.jpg&h=e424b427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以手足們<br />\n一方面要提升勇武心要有戰鬥意識<br />\n另一方面要創造多啲唔同有話題嘅和理非行動<br />\n<br />\n雙管齊下先有機會抗衡到咁強嘅對手<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n天佑吾城"},{"pid":"4e830ff22435471638cf4616303c14ec6b22ae97","tid":1591864,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"92c117dfd6d5d37b724cb3316d0a89f24267fe98","tid":1591864,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03344a512655a971d4837cd1346c183bb7a868b2","tid":1591864,"u